Uses of IComparator in suncertify.db.dao.comparator
 

Classes in suncertify.db.dao.comparator that implement IComparator
 class IntegerComparator
          IntegerComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as integers - it simply converts given strings to integer objects and invokes Integer.compareTo(java.lang.Integer) method.
 class MoneyComparator
          MoneyComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as money - it simply converts given strings to money objects and invokes Money.compareTo(Money) method.
 class TextComparator
          TextComparator is an implementation of comparator that compares string values as text - it simply invokes String.compareToIgnoreCase(String) method.
 

Methods in suncertify.db.dao.comparator that return IComparator
static IComparator ComparatorFactory.getComparator(DBType type)
          Returns IComparator instance for given database field type (DBType).
